ther: a box labeled “Anscochrome” with the word “ANSCOCHROME” below it, then a box labeled “Ansco” with the on-screen words “All-Weather Pan,” then a simple front view of a camera with the word “CAMERAS.” Finally, the Anscomatic projector appears inside the same lens circle with the word “ANSCOMATIC” beneath it, tying the projector to the broader Ansco camera and film line.",
